=================
Booster Generator
=================
 .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/boosterpacks.svg   
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/boosterpacks
 .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/Derfirm/booster_generator.svg?branch=master
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/Derfirm/booster_generator
 .. image:: https://landscape.io/github/Derfirm/booster_generator/master/landscape.svg?style=flat
    :target: https://landscape.io/github/Derfirm/booster_generator/master
    :alt: Code Health
 .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/boosterpacks.svg   
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/boosterpacks

To use (with caution), simply do::
    >>> from boosterpacks import *
    >>> cards = [(u'neut_u_modulehealer', u'1'), (u'terr_t_PrecisionStrike', u'2'), (u'terr_t_PulseBarrage', u'3'),(u'terr_t_NuclearStrike', u'4'),\
            (u'shan_u_NaninteSwarm', u'3'), (u'shan_t_CorruptTransform', u'3'), (u'shan_u_ParasiticThrall', u'5'), (u'shan_t_Infestation', u'2')]
    >>> boosterpack = BoosterGenerator(cards)
    >>> print (boosterpack.generate())

info.summary: Sample of boosterpack in Star Crusade
info.html_description:
To use (with caution), simply do::
>>> from boosterpacks import *
>>> cards = [(u'neut_u_modulehealer', u'1'), (u'terr_t_PrecisionStrike', u'2'), (u'terr_t_PulseBarrage', u'3'),(u'terr_t_NuclearStrike', u'4'),\
        (u'shan_u_NaninteSwarm', u'3'), (u'shan_t_CorruptTransform', u'3'), (u'shan_u_ParasiticThrall', u'5'), (u'shan_t_Infestation', u'2')]
>>> boosterpack = BoosterGenerator(cards)
>>> print (boosterpack.generate())
